## Description {#details}

Whether or not the instruction has greater than or equal to <code>Size</code> immediate successors.

If <code>HasIntermediary</code> is true, this tests also whether all successors of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sunit">SUnit</a> have greater than or equal to <code>Size</code> successors.
